events.message: add BANK Wallet to supported wallets list

events.body: I would remove all wallets from the BIP. It's hard to find a wallet which does not use BIP-44 nowadays and obviously, I don't want to maintain the list of all wallets in BIP-44.
@prusnak That has already been updated on the master branch via https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/770, and this PR now has conflicts, and can likely be closed.
